com.citytechinc.cq.component.annotations.widgets

Annotation Type Html5SmartImage


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value={FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface Html5SmartImage
    Represents a Widget of type CQ.html5.form.SmartImage in Classic UI The Smart Image is not supported in Touch UI and will render as a granite/ui/components/foundation/form/fileupload Widget

    • Optional Element Summary
